snippet.title: Swift: How to Fetch Contacts - Name & Phone Numbers (Ep 5)
snippet.description:
Retrieving contacts takes a couple of steps to do it successfully.  In today's lesson, I'll guide you through the necessary APIs to utilize to properly fetch the information for all contacts on your devices.  To make this lesson a little more interesting, we will also display phone number information on the bottom row of our cells.  This requires us to use a cell with a style of subtitle.  Enjoy.
